description:
Add .claude-plugin/marketplace.json at repo root to enable plugin via settings:

```json
{
  "name": "buddy-marketplace",
  "description": "Local marketplace for buddy-cli plugin",
  "owner": {
    "name": "Justin Sternberg"
  },
  "plugins": [
    {
      "name": "buddy",
      "source": "./claude-plugin",
      "description": "CI/CD pipeline management for Buddy.works",
      "version": "1.0.0"
    }
  ]
}
```

This allows enabling via settings instead of --plugin-dir flag.
